.playwright-mcp/

# ML artefacts — adapters, intermediate datasets, checkpoints,
# trained pointer-accel + long-jump models. Nothing in data/ml/ is
# shipped: every user trains their own homer-calibration models for
# their specific webcam / target / cursor setup (see README
# "Calibrating the homer for your setup"). Without local training
# the closed-loop servo still converges, it just iterates more.
data/ml/
*.safetensors
